This value set includes codes based on the following rules:

  • Import all the codes that are contained in http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/event-resource-types
  • Import all the codes that are contained in http://hl7.org/fhir/ValueSet/request-resource-types

name: Event Or Request Resource Types
title: EventOrRequestResourceTypes
description: This value set lists all the event or request resource types defined in this version of the specification.
